node.text: Spent the weekend celebrating our SIX year old 🥲😍❤️ Although I may have shed some tears with her turning 6 and starting kindergarten within a few weeks of each other this little girl really is turning into my bestie daily and I’m loving watching her grow into the little lady she is❤️ Gotta look at the pros right because ugh time sucks 😩😅#wheredmybabygo
